{
  "stem": "1222.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I got dressed up 1 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's time 5:30, and I came out with a-- with a holler.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I came into that committee.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I said, here's the piece of paper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I want to join your people, to cry, the [INAUDIBLE], the 7,000.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I'm one of them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I have to get in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't care the money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I went away, I put up a sign, wanted a ticket.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They-- they went up immediately to the police.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Was a lot of police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Was tight security.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they said, this is the man that we have to give him a chair.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Doesn't matter what it is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they're interviewing me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Maybe that's why you're here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You picked me, Susan, to come here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "If I wouldn't do this kind of stuff, you wouldn't be here, and that's exactly what's is going on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You have to push yourself to do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm not smart, but you have to have a drive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I would say again, I am not a nice man, because if I would be a nice man, the way I walked with my crippled father [SOB] and my two beautiful children, I should have gone to the ground, to the grave.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why would I run?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had to have the heart, the guts, to do that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's why I'm crying again and again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had the guts, and I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was lucky, and maybe somebody's watching me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Otherwise, how would I put in with my-- with the Israel people, and with my beautiful children, that beautiful memory would be nothing left.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's-- and I have to tell you, I'm thanking you very, very much.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
